ders while others, such as diplomatic relations or economic cooperation do not have such an effect"--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aAuthoritarianismzAsia. 0aChinaxForeign relationsy21st century. 0aChinaxForeign relationszCambodia. 0aCambodiaxForeign relationszChina. 0aChinaxForeign relationszBurma. 0aBurmaxForeign relationszChina. 0aChinaxForeign relationszMongolia. 0aMongoliaxForeign relationszChina. 0aRoutledge explorations in development studies.  aDS 779.47 B34 2015hUAHS-Bi0162035244357  aDS 779.47 B34 2015wLCc1i0162035244357d4/9/2015e3/3/2015lON_SHELFmUAHSSn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/26/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014032862bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/305822654